WEBVTT

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:30.532
Na nilianza na shule ya kiangazi.

00:03:31.960 --> 00:03:35.296
Utafiti unatuambia kuwa 
theluthi mbili ya pengo la ufaulu,

00:03:35.320 --> 00:03:37.656
ambayo 
ni tofauti katika upatikanaji wa elimu

00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:39.856
kati ya watoto matajiri na watoto maskini

00:03:39.880 --> 00:03:42.016
au watoto weusi na watoto weupe

00:03:42.040 --> 00:03:45.550
inaweza kuhusishwa moja kwa moja na 
upotevu wa elimu kipindi cha kiangazi

00:03:45.640 --> 00:03:48.456
Katika kaya maskini, 
watoto husahau karibu miezi mitatu

00:03:48.460 --> 00:03:50.536
ya walichosoma kipindi cha mwaka wa shule

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:51.896
wakati wa kiangazi.

00:03:51.920 --> 00:03:53.536
Wanarudi shule kipindi cha vuli,

00:03:53.560 --> 00:03:55.656
na walimu wao 
wanatumia miezi miwili mingine

00:03:55.656 --> 00:03:57.056
kurudia tena kuwafundisha.

00:03:57.080 --> 00:03:58.576
Hiyo ni miezi mitano.

00:03:58.600 --> 00:04:01.216
Mwaka wa shule Marekani ni miezi 10 tu.